plot: After two challenging missions, The Guardians of the Globe struggle to work as a team. Meanwhile, Mark tries to balance his hero duties, personal relationships, and his future as a college student.

Debbie tries to find a nanny for her new stepson, a nanny who isn't influenced by Cecil. Mark and Amber discuss their relationship issues with friends, Dupli-Kate is buried, and Allen returns to Earth with a request for help for Mark, who is trying to decipher his father's last cryptic request.—Gislef
